==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[AHD]]: /rōp/
*[[IPA]]: /rəʊp/
*[[SAMPA]]: /r@Up/

===Noun===
'''rope''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]; plural'' '''ropes''')
[[Image:rope.jpg|thumb|Rope wrapped around a pipe.]]

#(''uncountable'') Thick, strong [[string]] made of several [[strand]]s that have been twisted together.
#(''countable'') A length of this string.
#{{baseball}} A hard [[line drive]]
#: ''He hit a '''rope''' past third and into the corner.''

